<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Đăng Ký Tài Khoản</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[600px] border border-gray-700/50">
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 hidden md:block relative bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden md:border-r md:border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-purple-500/30 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite]"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/30 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-[spin_25s_linear_infinite_reverse]"></div>
            <div class="relative h-full flex flex-col justify-between p-12 text-white">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-wider">ADMINPRO</h1>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight">Quản lý chuyên nghiệp. Hiệu quả tối đa.</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300">Nền tảng của bạn để tự động hóa và tối ưu hóa mọi quy trình.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 sm:p-12 bg-gray-900 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Tạo tài khoản mới</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">Bắt đầu hành trình của Bro ngay hôm nay.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8">
            
                <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                    <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 text-red-300 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <i class="ri-error-warning-line"></i>
                        <span><%= error %></span>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <form class="space-y-6" action="/register" method="POST" id="register-form">
                    <div>
                        <label for="username" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-2">Username</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i class="ri-user-line absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-500"></i>
                            <input id="username" name="username" type="text" required placeholder="Chọn một username độc nhất" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg py-3 pr-4 pl-12 text-sm text-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 transition duration-200">
                        </div>
                        <div id="username-error" class="text-xs text-red-400 mt-2 hidden">
                            <i class="ri-error-warning-line align-middle"></i>
                            Username chỉ được chứa chữ, số, và dấu gạch dưới (_).
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-2">Email</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i class="ri-mail-line absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-500"></i>
                            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required placeholder="your.email@example.com" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg py-3 pr-4 pl-12 text-sm text-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 transition duration-200">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-2">Password</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i class="ri-lock-password-line absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-500"></i>
                            <input id="password" name="password" type="password" required placeholder="••••••••" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg py-3 pr-4 pl-12 text-sm text-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 transition duration-200">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="passwordConfirm" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-2">Xác nhận Password</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i class="ri-lock-password-line absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-500"></i>
                            <input id="passwordConfirm" name="passwordConfirm" type="password" required placeholder="••••••••" class="w-full bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg py-3 pr-4 pl-12 text-sm text-gray-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 transition duration-200">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full flex justify-center py-3 px-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm font-bold text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-gray-900 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-600/20 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                            Đăng Ký
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
                
                <div class="text-center text-sm mt-8">
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Đã có tài khoản?
                        <a href="/login" class="font-medium text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-500 hover:underline">
                            Đăng nhập ngay
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/client/register.js"></script>
</body>
</html>